annotationA: Augmin complex subunit dgt2; As part of the augmin complex, plays a role in centrosome-independent generation of spindle microtubules. The complex is required for mitotic spindle assembly through its involvement in localizing gamma-tubulin to spindle microtubules. dgt2 binds to microtubules in vitro
